title: Studio Tobac cigars with John Gazarro & Ryan Scholle
itunes:title: Studio Tobac cigars with John Gazarro & Ryan Scholle
description: This week, "The Honeymooner" John Gazarro and cigar roller Ryan Scholle from Studio Tobac, Oliva & Nub cigars joins us with some very special cigars from their 2013 Limited Edition Sampler. Old Fart Freddy is back, we examine why Cigar Aficionado continues to praise Cuba and their cigars, and ask... What makes a cigar "premium?"
